title: Celebrity Gossip Part 2 - Harry Styles Opens Up About Relationships
description: Harry Styles is Rolling Stone’s first global cover star and he’s talking about everything from his sexuality to his dedicated fan base. Plus, we finally know why Ben Affleck’s brother and JLo’s best friend weren’t at the wedding over the weekend.
